# JSDoc line length

When writing or editing JSDoc (and other block comments), keep **each line to at most 100 characters**.

- Wrap long lines onto the next line with the same comment prefix (e.g. ` * `).
- This applies to `/** ... */` blocks and to inline `/** ... */` on types/functions.
